- Use proper meta tags for all pages (title, description, keywords).
- Implement proper Open Graph tags for social media sharing.
- Use proper structured data (JSON-LD) for search engines.
- Implement proper canonical URLs to prevent duplicate content.
- Use proper heading hierarchy (h1, h2, h3, etc.) for content structure.
- Implement proper alt text for all images and media.
- Use proper URL structure and routing for SEO-friendly URLs.
- Implement proper sitemap generation and submission.
- Use proper robots.txt configuration for search engine crawling.
- Implement proper page loading speed optimization for Core Web Vitals.
- Use proper internal linking strategies for better site structure.
- Implement proper mobile-first responsive design.
- Use proper schema markup for rich snippets.
- Implement proper analytics and tracking for SEO performance.
- Use proper internationalization (i18n) for multi-language SEO.
